  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Liquor Store Simulator</strong> is a simulation game about developing your own store. You start your business in a small shop that you bought on credit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At first, it won’t be easy—you’ll have to work at the checkout yourself, accept deliveries, keep records, and maintain order in the sales area. But hard work and smart decisions will help you turn a modest retail outlet into a thriving store with a wide selection and satisfied customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase goods, arrange retail equipment as you see fit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/55b1e130389f1057d61c74d4bf21d717.poster.avif?t=1773839487\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/55b1e130389f1057d61c74d4bf21d717.webm?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/55b1e130389f1057d61c74d4bf21d717.mp4?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Draft Beer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel like a bartender. Pour customers the beer they desire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/5a2390a76eaf0efd606215416cb77014.poster.avif?t=1773839487\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/5a2390a76eaf0efd606215416cb77014.webm?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/5a2390a76eaf0efd606215416cb77014.mp4?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Staff Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At first, you’ll have to do everything yourself. But as your store grows, you won’t be able to handle it alone. Hire employees for efficient store management.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/491a14129193751637ed384230481fb9.poster.avif?t=1773839487\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/491a14129193751637ed384230481fb9.webm?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/491a14129193751637ed384230481fb9.mp4?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change the color of walls, ceilings, and floors. Make your store unique and unlike any other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/4b679d47db83e2236f84c5725a7e2268.poster.avif?t=1773839487\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/4b679d47db83e2236f84c5725a7e2268.webm?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/4b679d47db83e2236f84c5725a7e2268.mp4?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Liquor Store Simulator</strong> is a simulation game about developing your own store. You start your business in a small shop that you bought on credit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At first, it won’t be easy—you’ll have to work at the checkout yourself, accept deliveries, keep records, and maintain order in the sales area. But hard work and smart decisions will help you turn a modest retail outlet into a thriving store with a wide selection and satisfied customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase goods, arrange retail equipment as you see fit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/55b1e130389f1057d61c74d4bf21d717.poster.avif?t=1773839487\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/55b1e130389f1057d61c74d4bf21d717.webm?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/55b1e130389f1057d61c74d4bf21d717.mp4?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Draft Beer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel like a bartender. Pour customers the beer they desire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/5a2390a76eaf0efd606215416cb77014.poster.avif?t=1773839487\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/5a2390a76eaf0efd606215416cb77014.webm?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/5a2390a76eaf0efd606215416cb77014.mp4?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Staff Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At first, you’ll have to do everything yourself. But as your store grows, you won’t be able to handle it alone. Hire employees for efficient store management.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/491a14129193751637ed384230481fb9.poster.avif?t=1773839487\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/491a14129193751637ed384230481fb9.webm?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/491a14129193751637ed384230481fb9.mp4?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change the color of walls, ceilings, and floors. Make your store unique and unlike any other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/4b679d47db83e2236f84c5725a7e2268.poster.avif?t=1773839487\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/4b679d47db83e2236f84c5725a7e2268.webm?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124550/extras/4b679d47db83e2236f84c5725a7e2268.mp4?t=1773839487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
